file_content.text: I've got the door.
Where's Teeseven?
Where's that droid?
Generating false security alerts in other sectors. Capable little astromech-- Yes, I read you.
An updated timetable would be good.
Why? Is there a problem?
No, no problem...
...but we are starting to feel a bit exposed out here. How much longer do we have to--
Koth Vortena. He's our ride out of here.
Good, you got your precious Outlander. Now get her out the door, assuming she can stand.
Good, you got your precious Outlander. Now get him out the door, assuming he can stand.
Lana?
I patched him in. He can hear you.
Oh. Great. Welcome back.
Be patient, Koth, we're on our way--
I've seen her before....
No.
Hello.
We're not ready. Not for Vaylin.
I can feel her searching for me.
She is strong with the Force.
Her strength in the Force is astounding, even for her family.
It was like she looked right at us.
She could see us.
She sees you through the Force. You've become her quarry, and she never fails.
It's two against one. We're more than capable of--
We outnumber her.
Two of us, one of her. Trying to tell me we can't--
We can take her.
It's a wonder you're capable of standing right now. Go!
You don't have to tell me twice....
Then let's go.
Let's get you out of here. Hurry!
Skytroopers. Vaylin's far from alone.
I patched her in. She can hear you.
...but we are starting to feel a bit exposed out here. You find the Outlander yet?
Yes--I've patched her in.
Yes--I've patched him in.
Great--I'm Koth Vortena. Welcome to the most suicidal rescue mission in history. Hope you're everything Lana said you were.
Koth will fly us out of here, just as soon as we're through this door....
High Justice Vaylin! The... the intruders have released the Outlander. Skytroopers are scouring the building, but... uh....
But? Go on, don't be shy.
But there are alarms sounding in multiple sectors. We can't seem to pin them down.
Well... don't you worry.
Everybody makes mistakes.
